，啲on9黑社會又會出黎以為自己係保家衛國<br />\n<br />\n爭取真普選就係合法化爭取港獨，抗爭要有政治智慧啊！"},{"pid":"65688955031d591d8458b4847cda9c72f2b66d30","tid":1420931,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:49:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"401122dc4854e2bc388dcad0bc8ab12367858b99","tid":1420931,"uid":50284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"伍公子走到咁前，會唔會第二日被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f117d68f983c7c2f21566e1b4a4a912f51b0c4ae","tid":1420931,"uid":277044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"大家心入面都知要獨立.不過大部分人都未接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5d2f88d3ff9a7a16bafc5af6231b9739e4d99b","tid":1420931,"uid":153294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1729b2d4e4c56344d3212d566c45e7bfca5b584f","tid":1420931,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"有人話五大訴求先係初心，叫人唔好再衝擊，唔好搞警察，要對準政權。<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似有人將你鎖咗喺間屋入面，再放火燒屋。<br />\n<br />\n人地擺明想燒死你，你就不斷求佢俾鎖匙。<br />\n<br />\n我打算撞爆度門逃生，你就同我話勿忘訴求，鎖匙先係重點，唔好失焦。<br />\n<br />\n你仲期望個殺手會放過你？我跳窗都要搏下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>宜家香港人聽到革命，獨立就驚，話會得罪中共，又話香港無本錢。</strong><br />\n<br />\n乜大家唔係想出老解咩？咁點解又怕得罪中共？<br />\n<br />\n你哋究竟知唔知自己做緊乜？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你哋口口聲聲話要民主同自由，但係又唔敢抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢諗獨立，唔通你哋其實想感化共產黨？</strong><br />\n<br />\n建設民主中國仲難過搞港獨喎，香港人係咪仲要等中共施捨「民主」俾你？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你班左膠咁驚港獨，俾林鄭月娥話你港獨，你地就自我審查，要改口號。</strong><br />\n<br />\n咁不如由政府搞標語創作大賽，再等市民投稿俾政府，最後由林鄭選出勝利者好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其實，香港仲有險可守咩？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RYxFoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RYxFoe.jpg&h=67f7d746&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"我都係前線必睇！！！ 我都有睇直播 我拾階一年以上  唔好當大師神咁拜 （佢都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 佢今次比喻係唔完美  我贊成係要用其他方法出屋 罷工絕食  但拋磚放火係會令到整體示威者形象變差 亦畀機會人醜化我哋"},{"pid":"b31344993baa91fd146ec7f1567e89744f9ca73f","tid":1420931,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e5aa7101d1f185c6b3e3e1d4294c1f4eb7c148a","tid":1420931,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"3609eeec4d876ad7604ee6d9e78db76a66f56b15","tid":1420931,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"極權下無民主<br />\n你都唔會去魚蛋麵舖話要食Pizza啦下話"},{"pid":"ce8633da84ab71794f20428015282569dfa8741a","tid":1420931,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2e3deb4db368c2fc38e1e04201a32185879036","tid":1420931,"uid":181778,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"下佢地唔係不嬲都無賓周架咩？平日恰下平民就叻，做大事？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cf83fcd7a520635768c4bf873b1d5abd5e4197","tid":1420931,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2e3deb4db368c2fc38e1e04201a32185879036","tid":1420931,"uid":181778,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"踩jer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64249ff7528585434fe4e0c32078de2d2ad9e22","tid":1420931,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"左膠食屎，呃足港人三十年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895a275bae2b00354662e987195b5315949b9d5e","tid":1420931,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim